title: Ethnicity and Uninsured Status, 65 plus Population, Texas Counties, 2005
name: Ethnicity and Uninsured Status, 65 plus Population, Texas Counties, 2005
description: This is a dataset for County Estimates of the Uninsured for Texas from the Texas State Data Center and Office of the State Demographer. The original file contains five age groups, but for this map I chose to focus on the 65 plus age category to illustrate the aging of Texas counties which is a contributing factor in obesity numbers.

author.source: The Texas State Data Center and Office of the State Demographer
